# Spec-first Workflow

Use `.ai/skills/feature-spec.md` for non-trivial work, cross-package changes, architecture changes, API changes, database changes, or tasks likely to touch more than three implementation files.

Specs live in `.ai/specs/active/` while work is in progress and move to `.ai/specs/accepted/` when complete.
